<ion-header-bar class="background-positive">
	<button class="button button-icon ion-ios-arrow-back" ng-click="$ionicGoBack()"></button>
	<h1 class="title account-title" ng-class="marginleft">购买金币</h1>
</ion-header-bar>
<ion-view class="membership">  
  <ion-content>    
	<ion-scroll style="max-height:{{max_list_height3}}px">
		<div class="membership_buttons">
			<button class="button background-positive button-positive" ng-click="goCoinPayment(1500)">U币<span>1500枚</span>，￥98.00</button>
			<button class="button background-positive button-positive" ng-click="goCoinPayment(3000)">U币<span>3000枚</span>，￥198.00</button>
			<button class="button background-positive button-positive vip" ng-click="goCoinPayment(6000)">U币<span>6000枚</span>，￥398.00</button>
		</div>
		<h1 class="buy-coins">U币的作用</h1>
		<ion-item class="item-thumbnail-left">
			<img src="img/account/ic_present.png"/>
			<h2>赠送礼物</h2>
			<p>购买金币可以给你喜欢的人赠送礼物</p>
		</ion-item>
		<ion-item class="item-thumbnail-left">
			<img src="img/account/ic_cart2.png"/>
			<h2>U币商城</h2>
			<p>赠送的或礼物得到的U币，可在U币商城购买任何产品</p>
		</ion-item>		
	<ion-scroll>
  </ion-content>
</ion-view>
